Inspect or write repo config

Usage:
  agentflow config [flags]
  agentflow config [command]

Available Commands:
  effective   Inspect the merged effective config
  path        Print the repo config path
  show        Print the repo config file
  write       Write the sample repo config

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for config

Global Flags:
      --repo string   Path inside the repo to operate on

Use "agentflow config [command] --help" for more information about a command.
